shows.title: Army of Thieves
shows.overview: In this prequel to "Army of the Dead," a mysterious woman recruits bank teller Dieter to help her crew crack three legendary safes across Europe.

shows.title: Army of the Dead
shows.overview: After a zombie outbreak in Las Vegas, a group of mercenaries takes the ultimate gamble by venturing into the quarantine zone for the greatest heist ever.

shows.title: Betaal
shows.overview: Hired to displace tribal villagers to make way for a new highway, officials unearth an old curse and an army of British soldier-zombies.

shows.title: Bill Burr: I'm Sorry You Feel That Way
shows.overview: Bill Burr escapes the zombie apocalypse, explores how rom-coms ruin great sex and explains how too many childhood hugs may be the downfall of man.
shows.originalTitle: Bill Burr: I'm Sorry You Feel That Way

shows.title: Black Summer
shows.overview: A mother searches for her daughter as complete strangers band together to survive in the darkest hours of a zombie apocalypse.

shows.overview: Zack Snyder and his "Army of the Dead" team dive into the film's wild stunts, groundbreaking effects and the evolution of the zombie genre.
shows.originalTitle: Creating an Army of the Dead

shows.title: Dawn of the Dead
shows.overview: A gripping, gory remake of the cult horror classic: the undead walk the earth as flesh-eating zombies, trapping a disparate group of desperate people in a suburban shopping mall.

shows.title: Day of the Dead: Bloodline
shows.overview: A small group of military personnel and survivalists dwells in an underground bunker as they seek to find a cure in a world overrun by zombies.

shows.overview: When zombies and monsters invade his hometown, a scrappy 13-year-old orphan teams up with his friends in hopes of surviving the chaos.

shows.title: The Walking Dead
shows.overview: County Sheriff Rick Grimes, his wife, son and a small eclectic group try to survive constant attacks from zombies and other threats.

shows.title: iZombie
shows.overview: A medical student-turned-zombie tries to retain her humanity by eating brains at the morgue and finds she has an uncanny new gift for solving crimes.

shows.title: Zom 100: Bucket List of the Dead
shows.overview: In this anime adaptation, an overworked 24-year-old finally decides to live a little and create a bucket list, when a zombie outbreak hits the country.

shows.title: Zom 100: Bucket List of the Dead
shows.overview: Bullied by his boss, worked around the clock, he's nothing more than a corporate drone. All it takes is a zombie outbreak for him to finally feel alive!
shows.originalTitle: ゾン100～ゾンビになるまでにしたい100のこと～

shows.title: Resident Evil: Death Island
shows.overview: A t-virus outbreak in San Francisco leads to Alcatraz Island where a new evil has taken residence.
shows.originalTitle: バイオハザード：デスアイランド

shows.title: Onimusha
shows.overview: With a demonic, soul-consuming weapon in hand, can a legendary swordsman and a samurai brotherhood defeat a bloodthirsty zombie uprising?

shows.title: Train to Busan

shows.title: Zombieverse
shows.overview: In Seoul, where a zombie virus outbreak has run amok, who will outwit the undead in the face of challenging quests and come out alive?

shows.title: All of Us Are Dead
shows.overview: A high school becomes ground zero for a zombie virus outbreak. Trapped students must fight their way out — or turn into one of the rabid infected.
